                                Copy.


     With this option you can copy selected icon(s), If a drawer is 
selected the entire contents are copied. If the icon you selected is a 
disk icon then the diskcopy utility is automatically called. After copying 
icon(s) you get the name 'Copy_of_(Disk Name)' because you can't have the 
same name twice.



